          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the quesadillas are in the oven, cut the <strong>avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, around the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Remove the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a spoon and dice roughly</p><p>Trim, then slice the<strong> spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced avocado</strong> with the<strong> remaining chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> tangy avocado salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2477Step-7-x700.jpg",
